dogecoin.text: Let me be clear: I think he is a foul human, and I tho I think cryptocurrency is definitely an important road in the world of financing, I would never recommend anyone buy #dogecoin or any crypto unless you have money to waste because it is a very volatile investment, still. 10/

LO AND BEHOLD, today I wake up and read a bunch of news fully supporting my astrological theory. 😂 Bitch is gonna "fix" #dogecoin to make it the difi currency of the people or whatever. 8/ https://t.co/Llgz7xrIE3

But then, things kinda got off the rails, and he did the SNL thing feeling great and cool and then his appearance was totally trashed, along with his ego, and #dogecoin took a huge dive in value. Many people bailed ship. Not me! Why? 6/

My honest feeling is that Musk was just dicking around, enjoying his "power" being able to move difi markets with vague tweets about $doge, but then at some point, that Cancer nature kicked in and he started to KIND OF care about the under#doge crypto coin. 5/

Now, I have been following this $DOGE nonsense for months, after I used some savings on a dumb whim in February to buy some, because COVID 2020 broke my mind and it made sense at the time. I am in it to win it at this point, considering I have spent under $200. 4/
I have some things to say about astrology, Elon Musk and #Dogecoin. Predictions I gave a couple weeks ago to Mark, which have since come true. Hear me out... 😂1/
